            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;We are required to gather the information below to ensure you are not breaching any WTRT Regulations. Please tick each day you will be working and populate the employer and how much working time to take into account, this will ensure all work done is regulation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
